TextInput_1: I felt safe in the vehicle. At first the choppy way it turns was a bit concerning but this obviously is just part of the program and not something I should pay attention to!
I did not like that there wasn't much information displayed for me to see and that it wasn't showing me that it detected other things besides the people walking and their intentions.
I really liked that all of the information was displayed for me to see, it made me feel safe and able to trust the vehicle much more.

It appeared to run a stop sign at one point. I do not like that it doesn't show use of turn signals. I didn't understand why it was stopping at some places, one of them appeared to be at a stoplight but I couldn't really tell. All in all, that info could be useful, turn signal use and stop light and stop sign info.
The only problem  I can think of is the car did not stop at a stop sign towards the end of the trip.
Again, the vehicle didn't seem to stop at a stop sign toward the end. Other than that there were no problems.
